{{Main|{{ill|Nineteen-Level Cap and Rank System|ja|冠位十九階|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nineteen-Level Cap and Rank System|qq=|1=19 Cap Rank System|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11395034}}}}
